ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder authorizing the Amendments to Annex I and Annex II of the International Convention against Doping in Sport
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to accept, on behalf of the Government of Canada, that the AMENDMENTS TO ANNEXES I AND II OF THE INTERNATIONAL CONVENTION AGAINST DOPING IN SPORT, notified to the States Parties on October 1, 2022, be binding on Canada.
